Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw stepped out of the CR tank platform. She put her hand over her 
repaired shoulder, and looked at it. He looked around her environment, 
feeling out of place inside a ship. She felt like a feral beast inside it. 
She had forgotten the last time inside a bot-made vessel.

She looked around the interior. She heard no one, and smelt on one. She 
leered as she walked off into a hallway.
